{"tid":1071214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【無說話好講】強國大媽花園鋤地耕田 外籍女婿崩潰心血被毀","createTime":"2019-03-21T07:49:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T08:50:32.000Z","uid":225846,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"89cd7e1bb82bb88656de833ab583c9613136f258","tid":1071214,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:49:28.000Z","msg":"片 <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190320/59390822?utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=share_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190320%2F59390822%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&d=tFviIiuTv25K9aUiQ%2BXN3HGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=3fb58d9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190320%2F59390822%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&h=db7f4633\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190320/59390822?utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=share_link</a><br />\n<br />\n種菜可算是中國人的天賦本領，只要看到有空間，中國人都會把握機會種菜或其他植物。一名定居澳洲10年的中國人妻，前日在網上發佈影片，指母親竟將其外籍丈夫的花園，硬生生改成滿是芫茜、大蒜、生薑的菜園。老外女婿回家看到後，一面無奈。<br />\n<br />\n該名楊姓女子前日在網上貼出影片，瞬即吸引逾330萬網民觀看。楊姓人妻在居住的別墅後面菜地拍攝，指其母親正坐在辣椒樹下：「再不結都晚了，喲，都這麼大啦......」<br />\n<br />\n惟楊女士的外籍丈夫看到，花園原本的花卉植物全被拔走，面上卻露出一臉無奈的表情。楊女士亦哈哈大笑問丈夫：「Are you OK？（你還好嗎？）」丈夫只頭也不回地走向泳池。<br />\n<br />\n70後的楊女士表示，自己是地道北京人。10年前，她和來自英國的丈夫到澳洲悉尼定居，5年前買下了這幢別墅。丈夫平時會栽種花草，把花園打理得井井有條。早前，母親到悉尼暫住，幾個月內就把花園的植物斬掉，繼而種了番茄、扁豆、芫茜、大葱、大蒜等蔬菜。<br />\n<br />\n楊女士丈夫早前因工作經常早出晚歸，花園也疏於打理。直至前日，他突然心血來潮到花園看看，竟發現面目全非的「花園」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">柒頭娶大6婆 自己攞黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"a21f58df0f2da254bcc1d7d829016e2b0c86a71f","tid":1071214,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:52:08.000Z","msg":"娶支閪抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c8c7b8a07ea4e0de1aefecb067f6cff33c04022","tid":1071214,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:54:00.000Z","msg":"女婿咁老嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d13fa5bbf6eeecfc803919de8025b26d8949b5","tid":1071214,"uid":225846,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8c8c7b8a07ea4e0de1aefecb067f6cff33c04022","tid":1071214,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:54:00.000Z","msg":"女婿咁老嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:55:04.000Z","msg":"咪同香港啲廢老娶大6婆一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce7627a029348508df413383cfe08fb84e543260","tid":1071214,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:55:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e0e2c1ddc225ff6c746f1e40cf174bd3fd82d20","tid":1071214,"uid":21545,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:56:58.000Z","msg":"屌動物嘅後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38f09fdf3082d8e2887ad7112aef51e2ba26edac","tid":1071214,"uid":172169,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T08:01:37.000Z","msg":"外籍女婿猛鋤女兒後花園  強國大媽崩潰心血被毀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hk